plot: While Jack keeps having to rescue Lexi from a bumbling superhero, Zoe gets trapped while exploring an abandoned facility under the high school with her friends.

Carter's day begins with him catching Zoe planning to ditch school on encouragement from Lexi, He tells Zoe to go to school. While there she and two of her classmates finds an entrance under the school that leads to an old installation. Along the way they run into Zane who was sent by Thorne vie an air shaft to look for another way in. Eventually they get trapped and only have a few hours of air left. Carter runs into a guy in a costume who calls himself Captain Eureka, who bumbles around. Carter tries to find out who he is and stop before he does some real damage.—rcs0411@yahoo.com
